des: From Realtor and loan officer, Trey Van Dyke, The Real Report is a weekly 2 minute update on national economic and housing markets, plus information on the Sacramento, California real estate market. Keep up to date with the latest market news and be more knowledgeable in your real estate decisions! For personal descriptions, or if you or someone you know is looking to buy or sell real estate in Northern California, call Trey Van Dyke at (916) 932-TREY. CA DRE 02062439 | NMLS 1965225
